class gene:
    def __init__(self,chrom,strand,txStart,txEnd,exonStarts,exonEnds,name2):
        self.chrom=chrom
        self.strand=strand
        self.txStart=txStart
        self.txEnd=txEnd
        self.exonStarts=exonStarts
        self.exonEnds=exonEnds
        self.name2=name2
        
    def get_exons(self):
        exons=[[i,j] for i,j in zip(self.exonStarts,self.exonEnds)]
        return exons
    
    def get_introns(self):
        self.introns=[[i,j]for i,j in zip([self.txStart]+self.exonEnds,self.exonStarts+[self.txEnd])]
        return self.introns
    def get_strand(self):
        return self.strand
    
    def  get_TSS(self):
        self.TSS=self.txStart if self.strand=='+' else self.txEnd
        return self.TSS

#class and method
#--------------------------------------#
class gene:
    def __init__(self,chrom,strand,txStart,txEnd,exonStarts,exonEnds,name2):
        self.chrom=chrom
        self.strand=strand
        self.txStart=txStart
        self.txEnd=txEnd
        self.exonStarts=exonStarts
        self.exonEnds=exonEnds
        self.name2=name2
        
    def get_exons(self):
        exons=[[i,j] for i,j in zip(self.exonStarts,self.exonEnds)]
        return exons
    
    def get_introns(self):
        self.introns=[[i,j]for i,j in zip([self.txStart]+self.exonEnds,self.exonStarts+[self.txEnd])]
        return self.introns
    def get_strand(self):
        return self.strand
    
    def  get_TSS(self):
        self.TSS=self.txStart if self.strand=='+' else self.txEnd
        return self.TSS
    
class super_enhancer:
    def __init__(self,chrom,start,end,associated_genes=[]):
        self.chrom=chrom
        self.start=start
        self.end=end
        self.associated_genes=associated_genes


def smooth(data,step=1,window_width=5):
    index=0
    smoothed_data=[]
    while index+window_width<len(data)-1:
        smoothed_data.append(np.mean(data[index:index+window_width]))
        index+=step
    return smoothed_data


def read_data(path):
    y_min=0
    y_max=0
    T_or_N=''
    dic={}
    with open(path) as infile:
        data=[]
        for i in infile:
            if 'ymin' in i:
                y_min=float(i.strip().split('\t')[-1])
            elif 'ymax' in i:
                y_max=float(i.strip().split('\t')[-1])
            elif 'Tumor' in i:
                if T_or_N:
                    dic[T_or_N]=data
                data=[]
                T_or_N='Tumor'
            elif 'Normal' in i:
                if T_or_N:
                    dic[T_or_N]=data
                data=[]
                T_or_N='Normal'
            else:
                data.append([j for j in map(float,i.strip().split('\t'))])
        if T_or_N:
            dic[T_or_N]=data
    return y_min,y_max,dic
